{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"IDBEnvironment","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/IDBEnvironment","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/IDBEnvironment\"><code>IDBEnvironment</code></a></strong></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>警告：</strong>对于&nbsp;Firefox 52,&nbsp;the property defined in this mixin has been moved to the <code>WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope</code> mixin, and other browsers will follow suit. Look to that page for up-to-date <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/IndexedDB_API\">details. &nbsp;IndexedDB API</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/IndexedDB_API\">&nbsp;IndexedDB API</a>提供的帮助类<strong><code>IDBEnvironment</code></strong><code>包含了一个 indexedDB</code>&nbsp;属性，&nbsp;这个属性可以比较方便的操作 IndexedDB. 它是由<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>window</code></a> 和<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a> 实现的最顶级 IndexedDB 接口。</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> 此特性在 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Worker</a> 中可用</p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"idbenvironment.indexeddb_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/indexedDB\"><code>IDBEnvironment.indexedDB</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>该属性为应用程序提供了异步访问索引数据库 (IndexedDB) 的构件。它包含一个&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/IDBFactory\"><code>IDBFactory</code></a> 对象</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下述代码演示了如何创建一个异步打开数据库的请求，当该请求的<code>onsuccess</code>&nbsp;回调被执行时，该数据库被打开。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js;highlight:[3] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> db<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">openDB</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> DBOpenRequest <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>indexedDB<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"toDoList\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n DBOpenRequest<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onsuccess</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   db <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> DBOpenRequest<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">说明</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/IndexedDB/#idl-def-IDBEnvironment\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Indexed Database API 2.0<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">IDBEnvironment</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.IDBEnvironment","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参考","title":"参考","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IndexedDB_API/Using_IndexedDB\">如何使用 IndexedDB</a></li>\n <li>打开事务: <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/IDBDatabase\"><code>IDBDatabase</code></a></li>\n <li>使用事务: <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/IDBTransaction\"><code>IDBTransaction</code></a></li>\n <li>为键值设置范围: <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/IDBKeyRange\"><code>IDBKeyRange</code></a></li>\n <li>获取或修改数据库的数据: <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/IDBObjectStore\"><code>IDBObjectStore</code></a></li>\n <li>使用游标: <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/IDBCursor\"><code>IDBCursor</code></a></li>\n <li>参考示例：<a class=\"external\" href=\"https://github.com/mdn/to-do-notifications/tree/gh-pages\" rel=\" noopener\">To-do Notifications</a> (<a class=\"external\" href=\"https://mdn.github.io/to-do-notifications/\" rel=\" noopener\">view example live</a>.)</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"参考","id":"参考"}],"summary":"IndexedDB API提供的帮助类IDBEnvironment包含了一个 indexedDB 属性， 这个属性可以比较方便的操作 IndexedDB. 它是由window 和Worker 实现的最顶级 IndexedDB 接口。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"IDBEnvironment","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"IDBEnvironment","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/idbenvironment","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/idbenvironment/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/IDBEnvironment","title":"IDBEnvironment"}],"pageTitle":"IDBEnvironment - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}